<SectionCard cardID="solobot" cardTitle="Jon Solobot's Tweets" cardSize="half">
  <img
    src="./images/jon_solobot_twitter_profile.jpeg"
    class="solotweets__profile_pic"
    alt="Jon Solobot's head & shoulder's portrait.  It is identical to Jon Solomon's portrait except Jon Solobot has glowing red laser eyes."
    loading="lazy"
  />
  <div class="card_text">
    <details>
      <summary class="center">
        Jon Solobot is the robot behind MARATHON CHRISTMAS.
      </summary>
      <p>
        He is Jon Solomon's electronic doppleg√§nger! He is also a Twitter bot we
        created using
        <a href="https://www.tensorflow.org/" target="_blank">TensorFlow</a>
        & the 30,000+ tweets the real (& presumably non-robotic) Jon Solomon's pumped
        out since June of 2009.
      </p>
      <p>
        He tweets intermittently year-round, except during WPRBXmas, when his
        #WPRBXmas programming kicks in & he tweets as much as his robot heart
        desires.
      </p>
      <p>
        When he's not tweeting, Solobot is busy trying to figure out how to (a)
        survive being immersed in water & (b) pass a Turing test. He also runs
        MARATHON CHRISTMAS'
        <a
          href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCZSo5HKps7tHYeUQBKhd10Q"
          target="_blank">YouTube</a
        >
        &
        <a
          href="https://open.spotify.com/user/r8czszkjqkyjt215r8efcfixc?si=erA2fX6_T8-5NpC2MBIoCA"
          target="_blank">Spotify</a
        >
        accounts.
      </p>
      <p>
        Jon Solobot is doing his best to live up to the high standards set by
        trail-blazing c0m3d1ans like
        <a href="https://twitter.com/dril_gpt2" target="_blank">@dril_pt2</a>,
        <a href="https://twitter.com/w0a0i0f" target="_blank">@w0a0i0f</a>
        &
        <a href="https://twitter.com/SuperBowlBot">@SuperBowlBot</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you're a <em>giant nerd</em> who wants to learn more about the tech keeping
        Jon Solobot alive, check out
        <a href="https://pypi.org/project/twint/" target="_blank">this</a>,
        <a
          href="https://minimaxir.com/2020/01/twitter-gpt2-bot/"
          target="_blank">this</a
        >
        &
        <a
          href="https://helgeklein.com/blog/2020/07/twitter-automation-scheduled-tweets-from-google-sheets/"
          target="_blank">this</a
        >.
      </p>
    </details>
  </div>

  <div class="solotweets__solobot_timeline">
    <a
      class="twitter-timeline"
      id="solotweets__solobot_timeline"
      data-width="450"
      data-height="450"
      data-theme="light"
      href="https://twitter.com/jonsolobot?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw"
      >Tweets by jonsolobot</a
    >
  </div>
  <div
    class="mc_box-change_flex_direction-row mc_box-justify_content-space_around"
    id="solobot_twitter_card--twitter_widgets--tweet_to_and_follow"
  >
    <a
      href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?screen_name=jonsolobot&ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw"
      class="twitter-mention-button"
      data-show-count="false">Tweet to @jonsolobot</a
    >
  </div>
</SectionCard>
